---
title: Citrusy Shrimp Panzanella with Tomatoes and Fresh Mozzarella
description: What’s not to like about a salad that’s equal parts bread and veggies? This shrimp panzanella is bulked up by crunchy gem lettuce, juicy tomatoes, and fresh mozzarella. A lemon-garlic marinade gives these shrimp an extra flavor boost
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/56d5c2af4dab714f7e8b4567.jpg
